room_description: Dr. McCoy’s research is under threat from the large HMO, who wants to claim the credit and profit. Where can he turn? Who can help see that the cure gets into the right hands before it’s too late? McCoy has hidden the cure through a maze of clues and puzzles. Dr. McCoy has recruited your team to save the cure and research before it’s too late.
